<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">求首差1,尾合10的两个两位数的积时，可从较大首数的平方中减去其尾数的平方,此数即为所求之积。可利用公式</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">(10a+b)(10c+d)=10a×10a-b×b</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算，其中a、b分别是被乘数十位、个位上的数字。</Run>
    </Paragraph>

    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">61×59=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 61×59</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=60×60+1×1</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=3600-1</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=3599</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>